    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >对于那些热爱探索水下世界的人来说，<i>《Traíras》</i> 是一场适合全家人的激动人心且充满乐趣的冒险！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/57864f080a1da8743bb6c028a2f5a403.poster.avif?t=1758630398\" width=612 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/57864f080a1da8743bb6c028a2f5a403.webm?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/57864f080a1da8743bb6c028a2f5a403.mp4?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制勇敢的老虎鱼 <i>Tigerfish</i>，潜入一个五彩缤纷且引人入胜的旅程，探索充满秘密和奇异生物的海洋深处。游戏灵感来自巴西的<i>traíra</i>，一种聪明而凶猛的鱼，故事展现了一个具有挑战性但并不可怕的角色。<i>Traíra</i> 不是反派，而是有自然生存本能的生物。就像著名的食人鱼一样，<i>traíra</i> 是一个强大而无畏的捕食者，为水下环境增添了刺激和挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/a4e5b03252ce068c4e959ee8b412d8b2.poster.avif?t=1758630398\" width=612 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/a4e5b03252ce068c4e959ee8b412d8b2.webm?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/a4e5b03252ce068c4e959ee8b412d8b2.mp4?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>为什么要玩《Traíras》</i>？**</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>引人入胜且充满神秘感的故事情节</strong>：踏上一场充满惊喜的旅程，探索互相连接的环境，每一关都揭示更多关于 <i>Tigerfish</i> 冒险以及海洋生物多样性的内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/9fe22cee954615c3c2aea0bc58c00523.poster.avif?t=1758630398\" width=608 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/9fe22cee954615c3c2aea0bc58c00523.webm?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/9fe22cee954615c3c2aea0bc58c00523.mp4?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>身临其境的水下探险</strong>：潜入充满珊瑚迷宫、海洋洋流和隐藏角落的生动细致场景。游戏采用欢快的卡通风格，为所有年龄段提供友好且有趣的氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/9eba20a7147bd63028a465c40b09010b.poster.avif?t=1758630398\" width=608 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/9eba20a7147bd63028a465c40b09010b.webm?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/9eba20a7147bd63028a465c40b09010b.mp4?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>轻松又充满挑战的冒险</strong>：<i>《Traíras》</i> 将动作与宁静完美平衡，非常适合那些寻找轻松乐趣的玩家。面对强大的敌人，如螃蟹、河豚，以及凶猛的 <i>traíra</i>，为 <i>Tigerfish</i> 带来独特挑战，却不会令人害怕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/920b4879234275ab11b3bf34c5cb32dc.poster.avif?t=1758630398\" width=608 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/920b4879234275ab11b3bf34c5cb32dc.webm?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/920b4879234275ab11b3bf34c5cb32dc.mp4?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡通风格与手绘动画</strong>：灵感来自经典的2D游戏和传统动画，<i>《Traíras》</i> 拥有怀旧而温馨的视觉风格，非常适合成人和儿童共同享受。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/93beae89e76ea32a449ba80e473af71a.poster.avif?t=1758630398\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/93beae89e76ea32a449ba80e473af71a.webm?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335980/extras/93beae89e76ea32a449ba80e473af71a.mp4?t=1758630398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>献给大自然和海洋生物爱好者</strong>：每个环境都庆祝海洋的多样性，鲜艳的细节致敬海洋生物多样性——完美适合那些欣赏海洋美丽与奥秘的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你喜欢在游戏中探索海洋深处，并正在寻找轻松而引人入胜的冒险，那么 <i>《Traíras》</i> 将是你下一个挑战。征服险恶的水域，解锁秘密，征服深海！</p>",
